title: Ep. 295 - Klobuchar? I Hardly Know ‘Er!
description:
We analyze the official Warren and Klobuchar kickoffs. Then, Kasich yoga, Virginia Dems do minstrel shows, and the Grammys award people for neither singing nor dancing. Finally, the Pope pals around with the Grand Sheikh in Arabia, while Democrat congresswoman Ilhan Omar defames the Jews. Date: 02-11-2019
